Task 2 - Retail Sales EDA
🎯 Objective

To perform Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) on retail sales data and find useful business insights like sales trends, customer behavior, and revenue patterns.

📂 Dataset
Dataset used: Restaurant Sales (Tips Dataset)
Contains:
Total bill
Tip amount
Gender
Day of visit
Time (Lunch/Dinner)
Group size
🛠 Tools Used
Python 🐍
Pandas
Matplotlib
Seaborn
Google Colab
📊 Steps Performed
Loaded dataset and explored structure
Checked missing values
Performed basic statistical analysis
Analyzed total sales
Compared sales across days
Analyzed gender-wise spending
Studied tip behavior
Visualized data using graphs
🔍 Key Insights
Sales vary across different days
Dinner time has higher revenue than lunch
Customer spending differs based on gender
Tip amounts vary based on customer behavior
📌 Conclusion

This analysis helps understand customer behavior and sales trends, which can help improve business decisions and performance.
